---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profilePhoto from '../assets/Omar_Nataren_Picture.png';
---
<section id="sobre-mi" class="pt-8 pb-20 border-b border-black">
            <h2 class="section-title text-white animated-item">
                &gt; SOBRE_MÍ
            </h2>
            
            <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-x-10 gap-y-0">

                <div class="col-span-1 mt-8 md:mt-0 flex flex-col gap-6 animated-item">
                    <div class="w-64 md:w-full mx-auto md:mx-0 aspect-square bg-highlight rounded-md border border-white/10 overflow-hidden relative group flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 shadow-lg">
                        
                        <Image 
                            src={profilePhoto}    
                            alt="Foto de Omar Nataren" 
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
                        /> 
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-span-3 text-lg text-secondary space-y-6 animated-item text-left leading-relaxed flex flex-col justify-start">
                    <p>
                    Me llamo <span class="text-white font-medium">Omar Alejandro Nataren Arredondo</span> y comencé en el mundo de la tecnología participando y ganando olimpiadas de robótica a los 12 años. Actualmente genero soluciones de software enfocadas en crear <span class="text-white font-medium">experiencias de usuario, respaldadas por arquitecturas escalables</span> y eficientes.
                    </p> 
                    <p>
                        
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-span-2 text-lg text-secondary space-y-6 animated-item text-left leading-relaxed flex flex-col justify-start">
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <p>
                            Conversión de requerimientos funcionales complejos en <span class="text-white font-medium">interfaces gráficas intuitivas</span>, utilizando sistemas de diseño que aceleran el despliegue y garantizan una adopción fluida por parte del usuario final.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    
                    <div class="pt-2">
                        <a href="/downloads/Omar_Nataren_CV.pdf" target="_blank" download class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/50  text-white font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 group w-fit ">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-download text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
                            Descargar CV
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4. HIGHLIGHTS (NUEVOS: CON LINKS) -->
                <div class="col-span-2 mt-8 md:mt-0 flex flex-col gap-6 animated-item">
                    <div class="bg-highlight p-6 rounded-md border border-white/10 shadow-lg hover:border-white/30 transition-colors h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5 text-white border-b border-white/10 pb-2 flex justify-between items-center">
                            TOP ACHIEVEMENTS
                            <i class="fas fa-trophy text-yellow-500/50"></i>
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="text-secondary text-sm space-y-6">
                            
                            <!-- Highlight 1: Capital One Winner (Con Link) -->
                            <li class="group">
                                <a href="https://hackathon.genius-arena.com/hackathon/finanzas-para-un-futuro-sostenible-capital-one-mexico/" target="_blank" class="cursor-pointer flex items-start gap-4 p-3 -m-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/5 transition-all">
                                    <div class="mt-1 min-w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(250,204,21,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong class="text-white flex text-lg mb-1 items-center gap-2">
                                            1st Place Winner - Talent Land 2025
                                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt text-xs text-secondary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity transform translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-y-0"></i>
                                        </strong>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-white/50 block font-light">Capital One Track: Finanzas para un Futuro Sostenible</span>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                            </li>

                            <!-- Highlight 2: NASA Space Apps (Con Link) -->
                            <li class="group">
                                <a href="https://brunoespina1.github.io/nasa_orrely_chilitos/" target="_blank" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-3 -m-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/5 transition-all">
                                    <div class="mt-1 min-w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(59,130,246,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform"></div>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong class="text-white text-lg mb-1 flex items-center gap-2">
                                            NASA Code Challenge - Space O'Reilly Project
                                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt text-xs text-secondary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity transform translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-y-0"></i>
                                        </strong>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-white/50 block font-light">Plataforma educativa 3D Interactiva & Social Impact</span>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                            </li>

                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>